    "Frontiers in Artificial Intelligence 13 frontiersin.org from 2022 to 2023.",
    "By 2023, an estimated 500,000 deepfake videos were shared on social media.",
    "As deepfakes become more common and harder to detect, the necessity of robust countermeasures grows.",
